origin_prompt.content:
你能够调用以下的API:
{'name': 'IntelAPI.analyze_success_rate', 'description': 'This function analyzes the success rate of R&D projects in specified technologies based on the provided project data.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'project_data', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The R&D project data to be analyzed.'}, {'name': 'technology', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The specific technology area, e.g., semiconductor manufacturing, nanotechnology.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'success_rate', 'description': 'The success rate of the R&D projects in the specified technology area.'}]}
请用以下格式进行回复:
想法: 你这一步的目标
动作: 你要调用的API名称
动作参数: JSON格式的参数输入,全部写在一行
调用工具 IntelAPI.analyze_success_rate, 它的参数输入如下: 'project_data'是'Intel's R&D project data', 'technology'是'semiconductor manufacturing and nanotechnology'.
